  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Breaking things adds to your power.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Half-orc or orc, rage class feature.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>When you are raging and you succeed at a sunder combat maneuver, you regain 1 round of rage. If the sunder attempt causes the object to gain the broken condition, you heal 1 hit point. You can only gain these benefits once per round.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>You can spend 2 stamina points to regain 1 round of rage after reducing a foe whose CR is at least half your character level to below 0 hit points, rather than upon successfully sundering a target.",
